<p>Hi I have some troubles with a "margin" in mozilla, explorer, safari and chrome for IOS.</p>  <p>For Mozilla and Explorer I solved with</p>  <pre><code>/*Styles for Firefox*/ @-moz-document url-prefix() {     .box img {         width: 100%;     }  .box .info{     margin-left: -70% !important;} }  /* Styles for IE10*/ @media screen and (-ms-high-contrast: active), (-ms-high-contrast: none) {     .box img {         width: 100%;     }      .box .info{    margin-left: -70% !important;} } </code></pre>  <p>What about Safari? </p>